      <title>据 Matichon 报道，泰国前总理他信获皇家特赦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/former-thai-pm-thaksin-gets-royal-amnesty-matichon-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《泰国日报》报道，为庆祝泰国国王哇集拉隆功的生日，泰国前总理他信·西那瓦等 5 万多名囚犯和重罪犯将获得特赦，但该报并未透露这一消息来源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/former-thai-pm-thaksin-gets-royal-amnesty-matichon-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 08:24:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列袭击黎巴嫩南部至少造成 10 名叙利亚人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-17/woman-and-two-children-among-10-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-southern-lebanon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黎巴嫩纳巴提赫（美联社）——据黎巴嫩卫生部称，以色列周六凌晨对黎巴嫩南部发动的袭击造成至少 10 名叙利亚国民死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-17/woman-and-two-children-among-10-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-southern-lebanon</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 08:16:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克里姆林宫将乌克兰入侵视为自然灾害</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/kremlin-is-treating-ukraine-s-kursk-incursion-like-a-natural-disaster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是 80 年来外国军队首次在俄罗斯领土上作战，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京星期五在例行安全委员会会议上召集高级官员听取国防部长安德烈·别洛乌索夫的报告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/kremlin-is-treating-ukraine-s-kursk-incursion-like-a-natural-disaster</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国经济在上半年“顺利”后开始放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/uk-economy-heads-for-slowdown-after-goldilocks-first-half</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国经济正处于“金发姑娘时刻”，通胀放缓、就业上升、增长健康，这可能为英格兰银行和基尔·斯塔默政府创造更舒适的环境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/uk-economy-heads-for-slowdown-after-goldilocks-first-half</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数字欧元让德国人担心他们的钱不安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/digital-euro-has-germans-fretting-their-money-won-t-be-secure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在距离法兰克福约 100 公里（62 英里）的一个风景如画的葡萄酒小镇，隐藏着一座掩体，几十年来一直是德国最保密的秘密之一。这座巨大的建筑建于 1962 年，里面存放着替代的德国马克，以防西德的冷战对手向市场大量投放假钞，引发恶性通货膨胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/digital-euro-has-germans-fretting-their-money-won-t-be-secure</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯将与卡车司机工会会面，争取劳工支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/harris-to-meet-teamsters-union-as-she-courts-labor-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据她的竞选团队称，美国副总统卡玛拉·哈里斯已接受国际卡车司机兄弟会领导层的邀请参加圆桌讨论。]]></description>
