    <item>
      <title>印尼庆祝新首都落成</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/indonesia-celebrates-nusantara-a-new-capital-struggling-to-take-shape</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚将在婆罗洲岛偏远丛林中建造尚未完工的未来首都，但资金困难、错过最后期限以及国家领导层的变动给这个耗资数十亿美元的项目带来了压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/indonesia-celebrates-nusantara-a-new-capital-struggling-to-take-shape</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
